  section.highlights
    .container.container-narrow
      .row 
        .col-md-6
          i.icon.icon-code
          span.h1 Use the Libraries You Love
          p.lead Aerobatic is a platform, not a framework. Build your app with AngularJS, Ember, React, Backbone, jQuery, and whatever next best thing comes along. We're not out to re-invent the wheel, just provide a smoother surface to roll on.

        .col-md-6
          i.icon.icon-window
          span.h1 Built for modern web apps
          p.lead Designed from the ground-up for today's web apps. Everything a front-end developer needs including: command line deployment, API integration and key management, authentication, SEO and more come right out of the box.
          a.btn.btn-default.btn-fancy.features(ng-href="/features") 
            i.icon-cog-alt
            span Features

